summary: This is a travel voucher approval notification for a trip related to the Epstein investigation. It documents approved expenses for a trip to Beverly Hills, CA for witness interviews in February 2020.

events.title: Epstein Investigation Witness Interviews Trip
events.description: Travel for witness interviews related to the Epstein investigation took place in Beverly Hills, CA.

keyFacts: A travel voucher (ID: 11061409-1) was approved on March 24, 2020, for expenses related to the Epstein investigation.
The trip purpose was 'R20NYS13400 - Epstein Investigation Witness interviews'.
The travel occurred from February 26 to February 29, 2020, with a destination of Beverly Hills, CA.
The voucher total expenses were $1,196.11 against an estimated trip cost of $1,634.37.
The document indicates ongoing investigative activity related to the Epstein case in early 2020.
